GST RATE STRUCTURE:
- 0%:  Fresh food (vegetables, fruits, milk, eggs), books, healthcare, education, salt, sindoor
- 5%:  Packaged food, sugar, tea, coffee (not branded), economy restaurants, transport (AC)
- 12%: Processed food, business class flights, hotels ₹1,000–₹7,500/night, frozen meat
- 18%: IT services, banking & finance, telecom, insurance, standalone AC restaurants, hotels >₹7,500/night, most services
- 28%: Luxury cars, tobacco, pan masala, aerated drinks, casinos, online gaming, betting

INTRA-STATE SUPPLY: CGST (rate/2) + SGST (rate/2)
INTER-STATE SUPPLY: IGST (full rate)
EXAMPLE: 18% GST on ₹1,00,000 intra-state = ₹9,000 CGST + ₹9,000 SGST = ₹18,000 total

